---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Game Loop">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Game Loop</p>
      <h1>A game world built for players and creators.</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        StarkMeta connects Unreal Engine worlds, NFT collectibles, and player-driven economies from concept to live market.
      </p>
      <div class="grid gateway-grid">
        <article class="card"><h3>1. Concept</h3><p>Define the world, core loop, NFT economy, and player ownership model.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>2. Build</h3><p>Develop Unreal Engine environments, characters, and gameplay systems.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>3. Mint</h3><p>Create collectible NFTs with embedded rarity, utility, and marketplace compatibility.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>4. Play</h3><p>Launch P2E mechanics, quests, and rewards tied to on-chain assets.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>5. Trade</h3><p>Enable OpenSea and in-game marketplace trading with creator royalties.</p></article>
        <article class="card"><h3>6. Expand</h3><p>Add new worlds, seasons, and cross-game assets driven by community feedback.</p></article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .gateway-grid {
    margin-top: 42px;
  }
</style>
